    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="948204977">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-948204977" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-948204977" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="948204977">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/high_way1988/">Highway 1988</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-08-08</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">论文集的弊处便是重言太多</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="873425561">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-873425561" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-873425561" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="873425561">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4058013/">若存</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-12-20</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">写的最好的两篇是当代治学方法的进步与古今文史观念的演变，前者剖析二陈有意义的史学很到位，后者则体现出周氏治唐人小说的渊源和目的。陈允吉朱刚两位先生所写书评也很到位，所谓典范尤在陈寅恪。又从书中引“书之重，辞之复，其中必有美者焉”一句，极为得体，若能删去复重，当然更好。讲胡小石先生文章多轶闻，有趣。2016.9.10。二刷。重点尤在陈寅恪。具体体现在以家世、师承讨论学术渊源这一方面。论陈氏本人的著作，从其家族薰习出发，论黄侃《文心雕龙札记》的撰作，也是着眼于章、刘两位背后的师承，一属朴学家，一属文选派，黄氏则以刘为主，折衷两者，见《原道篇》札记。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1105691113">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1105691113" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1105691113" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1105691113">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/95678880/">月落琴张</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-02-17</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">本书里陈寅恪的那几篇写得非常好，而《师门问学录》里周勋初也说现在的“近代学者研究”大都作得不好，估计是想说就他自己作得还不错吧。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="741585480">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-741585480" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-741585480" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="741585480">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ricoeur/">ariosto</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-12-31</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">这本作为2013最后读完的一本书吧。增订量很大，几乎翻一番，并附了一些名篇。可反复研读。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="797544212">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-797544212" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-797544212" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="797544212">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/49443595/">Big Bod</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-04-27</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">知人论世，对学术大家之成就梳理熨帖；以意逆志，于学术经典之特色解读到位。鉴往以知今，通变以开来，对当下学界之反思颇为到位。了解近当代学术研究不可忽略之作。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

