    <div class="main review-item" id="5996656">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5996656/" class="title-link">当代学术史必读书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5996656"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/73175977/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/73175977/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">dlorchid</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-05-30"
      class="main-meta">2013-05-30 10:39:48</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5996656_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  最喜欢这本书的知人论学。文史学界几位成就卓著的学术大家黄侃、胡小石、陈寅恪、朱东润、罗根泽、程千帆等，周勋初先生与他们或有亲密接触，或是熟悉他们的为人，因这一特殊身份和机缘，所以书中内容亦极具学术史研究史料价值。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5996656_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5996656_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





